<br>
Cresting a hill in the Eastern Commons, I too heard the strange callings and chants of Darkmoon ... particularly a female like voice.  The siren like voice challenged me to appear at the &quot;tunnel&quot; and of course it got the better of a curious gnome.<br>
<br>
But be a gnome of little wisdom i am not ...<br>
<br>
Me sneak my way into the darkened tunnel with a crowd of human types ... closely skirting the evil Dark one.   Once at a safe vantage point , me sees that see cloaks her strength from my eyes and challenges but a poor little gnome.  I bravely appear in front of her and there begins a battle of tongues and wit not often heard outside of an Ak'anon mechanics shop.  <br>
<br>
She calls herself Xdria and a knight of such I have never stood in front of before with such trembling knees ... ( I later find out through the underworld that she be of 43 crops ) ... So , I stood my ground even as she turned her tempting back to me in jest and called me a coward ( a smart coward be me though )<br>
<br>
Her strength and armor were no match for my tongue , as quick as a fireball and she turned , head down ...<br>
<br>
Me promises to do her a favor as I leave ... me will pull the dagger out of her back as she lies bleeding on the killing fields ...<br>
<br>
Timo Nas <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ujoekercapraidcu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Joeker Capraid Cu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lad/Lass</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#330000>(4/20/01 3:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re</span><hr size=1>    I have heard this dark ones name spoken amongst me clan far too often...<br>
