<br>
Later in this same eve, another dark spawn of Darkmoon entered Nagafen's Lair, which some of the family happened to be hunting. Racing to this dark one, he turned tail and quickly disappeared into the Lavastorm Mountains. It is now my belief, these dark elves will only fight when the odds are in thier favor. More the better for myself, it just means less running around. I can and will dispatch a few at a time that way. Thier time is running short, and I feel they know it as well.<br>
